	- readfile/writefile in binmode

  * lib/cmt/test.pm:
	add cps()

  * lib/cmt/table.pm:
	add |-style table file parser

  * lib/cmt/oop.pm:
	- unified the lex/lexer/yylex name convention
	- add debug options to yparser->() returned by oop_newparser

  * lib/cmt/: oop_mod.pm, oop_y.pm, oop_y.y:
	add support of %lexer, %yylex attributes.
	add debug options to yparser->() returned by oop_newparser

  * lib/cmt/lexutil.pm:
	- unified the lex/lexer/yylex name convention
	- if the last token __xxx is returned after EOF, then the token is changed to EOF-token.
	- moved lex_dump from cmt::oop to cmt::lexutil

