  * lib/cmt/ios.pm:
	add cmt::ios::merged derivation:  when multiple cmt::ios were created, they have to be 'loop'ing in separated threads, this cause many problems.  the new merged-model allows one to 'loop'ing in one thread, by IO::Select all the sockets of cmt::ios(s).

